high_descs: Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the black shelves on the wall.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the black shelf in front of you.
Turn around and walk over to the black chair in the corner of the room.
Put the credit card on the front left corner of the seat of the chair.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the couch.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the couch.
Turn right and walk over to the chair in the corner of the room.
Put the credit card on the seat of the chair to the right of the card that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the seat of a black chair.

high_descs: Turn around, go across the room to the shelves.
Pick up the credit card that is on the top shelf to the right of the vase.
Turn around and go to the black chair.
Put the credit card in the chair.
Turn to the left and go to the cardboard box on the couch that is on the right.
Pick up the credit card that is on the couch to the right of the cardboard box.
Turn to the right, go to the wall, turn to the left, go forward and turn around.
Put the credit card on the chair to the right of the other credit card.
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards in a chair.

high_descs: Turn around and walk straight to the small table in the corner of the room
Pick up the credit card from the shelf above the table and next to the vase
Turn around and walk straight to the chair
Place the credit card on the seat cushion of the chair
Turn to the left and walk straight to the middle of the sofa then turn right and face it
Pick up the blue credit card from the sofa seat cushion
Turn to the right and walk straight to the chair and turn to face it
Place the credit card on the seat cushion of the chair
anns.task_desc: Put two credit cards on a chair seat cushion
